    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简介</h2>Puzzle GO!是一款休闲益智类的拼图游戏，玩家通过使用单击鼠标来调整图块位置以还原图片。本作为玩家提供了多张精美图片作为关卡。游戏同时还为玩家精心准备了丰富的成就系统内容。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创意工坊</h2><strong><i><u>创意工坊功能已经正式上线</u></i></strong>！测试期间已经有很多朋友上传了精致的拼图内容，赶快来游玩吧!本作还会不定期推出创意工坊主题悬赏活动，欢迎小伙伴们参加！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成就橱窗</h2>本作由于刚刚发布，成就橱窗暂时还不能使用，十分抱歉，请宁耐一时！之后还会上架给大家丰富的动态头像、STEAM表情包和steam资料背景，绝对保证大家买不了吃亏买不了上当，谢谢各位！<br>欢迎加入游戏交流群：<br>   ❤QQ交流群：814819327 ❤<br>如果您有什么想法，想要作者增加在未来的点数商店和成就中，可以在群里留言，我们会综合玩家意见来增加点数商店及成就里的内容。谢谢您的支持！<br><br>目前已经上线了许多精美的成就，例如：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382260/extras/d9ea7010b781e8c9a79e0bc4afee0220.avif?t=1688480404\" width=514 height=78 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382260/extras/87a0e5ec6c0b5fbbb08ba708c561ba5d.avif?t=1688480404\" width=518 height=114 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382260/extras/ae5331443ab182d9375d9bf23e8dbb03.avif?t=1688480404\" width=536 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382260/extras/866cf532fd332058f7811beddb22b39e.avif?t=1688480404\" width=536 height=68 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382260/extras/9ab7bf8a329606dd13e9cce4841db087.avif?t=1688480404\" width=534 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382260/extras/4549642c35f2580d4033125232a709fb.avif?t=1688480404\" width=544 height=562 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/23822